&lt;dt>间质性肺疾病（interstitial lung diseases，ILDs）| 弥漫性实质性肺疾病（diffuse parenchymal lung disease，DPLD）&lt;/dt>
&lt;dd>一组以主要累及&lt;strong>肺间质和肺泡腔&lt;/strong>，导致肺泡-毛细血管功能单位丧失的弥漫性肺疾病。&lt;/dd>
&lt;dd>临床主要表现为&lt;span class="inline-list">&lt;span class="inline-list-item">&lt;strong>进行性加重的呼吸困难&lt;/strong>、&lt;/span>&lt;span class="inline-list-item">&lt;strong>限制性通气功能障碍&lt;/strong>伴&lt;strong>弥散功能降低&lt;/strong>、&lt;/span>&lt;span class="inline-list-item">低氧血症&lt;/span>&lt;span class="inline-list-conjunction">以及&lt;/span>&lt;span class="inline-list-item">影像学上的双肺弥漫性病变&lt;/span>&lt;/span>。&lt;/dd>
&lt;/dl></description></item><item><title>特发性肺纤维化</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E9%97%B4%E8%B4%A8%E6%80%A7%E8%82%BA%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E7%89%B9%E5%8F%91%E6%80%A7%E8%82%BA%E7%BA%A4%E7%BB%B4%E5%8C%96/</link><pubDate>Thu, 24 Nov 2022 10:50:36 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E9%97%B4%E8%B4%A8%E6%80%A7%E8%82%BA%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E7%89%B9%E5%8F%91%E6%80%A7%E8%82%BA%E7%BA%A4%E7%BB%B4%E5%8C%96/</guid><description/></item><item><title>结节病</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E9%97%B4%E8%B4%A8%E6%80%A7%E8%82%BA%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E7%BB%93%E8%8A%82%E7%97%85/</link><pubDate>Thu, 24 Nov 2022 11:42:48 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E9%97%B4%E8%B4%A8%E6%80%A7%E8%82%BA%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E7%BB%93%E8%8A%82%E7%97%85/</guid><description/></item><item><title>过敏性肺炎</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E9%97%B4%E8%B4%A8%E6%80%A7%E8%82%BA%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E6%80%A7%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E/</link><pubDate>Thu, 24 Nov 2022 11:42:57 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E9%97%B4%E8%B4%A8%E6%80%A7%E8%82%BA%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E6%80%A7%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E/</guid><description/></item><item><title>肺血栓栓塞症</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E8%A1%80%E6%A0%93%E6%A0%93%E5%A1%9E%E7%97%87/</link><pubDate>Sat, 19 Nov 2022 12:00:07 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5